description:
This is a 304 minute workout called 'Unofficial Disney Cruise Line Playlist' from the channel Carly Steele Johnson.
The workout falls under Cardio/Walking.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You won't need any equipmentThe workout has a The Mindful Walk and The Nature Flow vibe.
The The Mindful Walk vibe means Meditative, story-driven, immersive. This is especially good for When you need fresh air, a change of pace, and mental clarity. The The Nature Flow vibe means Breath-centered, full-body, outdoor rhythm. This is especially good for When you want fresh air, nature, and full-body movement..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: Playlist Name: Unofficial Disney Cruise Line Playlist
Description: Close your eyes and pretend you're walking the ship, chilling on Castaway Cay, or at one of the shows! I cruise at least once a year, and take notes on what I hear. Any new songs are added (exlcluding holiday) after.
